CoinDesk,is,an,information,center,on,Bitcoins,a,decentralized,digital,currency,used,around,the,world,One,service,that,CoinDesk,provides,is,the,Bitcoin,Price,Index,BPI,This,Bitcoin,pricing,data,is,calculated,every,minute,and,is,published,in,USD,EUR,and,GBP,BPI,data,is,made,available,programmatically,via,REST,API,People,can,use,the,API,however,they,like,as,long,as,they,credit,CoinDesk,as,the,data,source